Package: caraneer-config-postgresql
Version: VERSION_REPLACEME
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends:postgresql-17 | postgresql-16 | postgresql-15 | postgresql-14, simconf (>=0.3.7), simconf (<<0.5.0), jq
Maintainer: Aritz Beobide-Cardinal <aritz@caraneer.ca>
Description: Caraneer opinionated PostgreSQL config with replication support
 This package configures PostgreSQL with managed WAL settings,
 logical or physical replication, and optional replica initialization.
 It uses simconf to render configuration templates via debconf input.
